cognic-test-mcp-pack-fixture-sigstore-bundle-placeholder
this file is intentionally non-cryptographic for Sprint-5 unit tests
the T9 persister treats Sigstore bundle bytes as opaque — its only
contract is "persist atomically with 7-year retention metadata".
The @pytest.mark.cosign_real integration path uses build_test_
attestations.sh --regenerate to produce a real Sigstore bundle.
